songs.title: Cosmic Lelos
songs.lyrics:
'So many years ago....
In a land called Sabinas.... '
Listen, My Son

Plastilina has the beat

Plastilina has the girls
Plastilina has the cars
Plastilina has the money
Plastilina has the beers

Plastilina has the beat

Le Hammond Inferno has the beat
Bertrand Burgalat has the beat
Dj K has the beat
UFO has the beat....
But

Plastilina has the beat

'....And that's the story, My Son'
